For cursor, vscode or antigravity

1. Install IDE
2. Install extensions: c/c++, go, python, vim emulation, opencode, claude code, codex(chatgpt)
4. Sign in to opencode, claude code and openai
5. File -> Preferences -> Keyboard Shortcuts, refer to system-key-shortcut
6. Press <ctrl+shift+p> and search <preferences: open user settings (json)>, refer to vim-extension-config
